  "short_description": "The Ubiquiti Protect Floodlight (UP-FloodLight) is an advanced lighting solution designed for outdoor use, featuring robust weatherproofing with an IPX5 rating.",
  "description": "The Ubiquiti Protect Floodlight (UP-FloodLight) is an advanced lighting solution designed for outdoor use, featuring robust weatherproofing with an IPX5 rating. It offers a blend of plastic and metal construction, ensuring durability against environmental elements. The device provides bright illumination with its LED lights and incorporates intelligent features such as motion detection. It's powered via PoE (Power over Ethernet) for easy installation and connectivity. The Protect Floodlight integrates seamlessly with the UniFi Protect system, allowing for remote management and control through both web and mobile applications, enhancing security and convenience around your property",
  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "LED Floodlight with a Motion Sensor",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti Protect Floodlight (UP-FloodLight) is an advanced lighting solution designed for outdoor use, featuring robust weatherproofing with an IPX5 rating. It offers a blend of plastic and metal construction, ensuring durability against environmental elements. The device provides bright illumination with its LED lights and incorporates intelligent features such as motion detection. It's powered via PoE (Power over Ethernet) for easy installation and connectivity. The Protect Floodlight integrates seamlessly with the UniFi Protect system, allowing for remote management and control through both web and mobile applications, enhancing security and convenience around your property\n\nFeatures:\n\nIntense 550 lumens of LED light\nWall-mountable\nPairs with UniFi Security Camera\nMotion detection\nWall Mountable\nWeatherproof (outdoor exposed)\nConnect and power using PoE\n\nUniFi Protect is required to run this product with full functionality. Recommended using it with the UniFi Dream Machine Pro or the UniFi Protect Network Video Recorder."
    }
  ],
